item.title: Who?
item.description: There are lot of lucky people who are sharing Year Zero with me. You know who you are. I won’t name people I know personally but I will name famous people, to make myself feel a bit better. Real People Sarah Michelle Gellar Liv Tyler Jessica Chastain Michael Fassbender Zachary Quinto Tom Hardy Fictional People Jessica Drew aka Spider Woman Carol Danvers aka Ms Marvel aka Captain Marvel Judge Dredd Things Voyager 1 and 2 spacecrafts Apple II home computer Star Wars Discoveries Wow!
